title: Choosing Life: Surviving a Medical Abortion - Claire Culwell
description:
Like most people, Claire Culwell never thought abortion would impact her - until the day that she found out her mother tried to kill her in the womb. Claire tells the story of her discovery that she survived an abortion that killed her twin and the impact this discovery had on the course of her entire life.
